Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:56.00,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}或許我想要永遠這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.01,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}這份感情已溶於我心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:08.68,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我們一直在尋找  那顆成對的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:16.81,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我們一直在相互訴說  那不成文的一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:24.95,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}透過掌心的溫暖  直擊內心的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:33.04,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我一直在逞強  看著像個小大人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:36.67,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想要更了解你
